#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.64"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.64:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.64:0.2"
msgid "7. Saññāvagga"
msgstr "7. Perceptions"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.64:0.3"
msgid "64. Dutiyavaḍḍhisutta"
msgstr "64. Growth (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.64:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamānā ariyasāvikā ariyāya vaḍḍhiyā "
"vaḍḍhati, sārādāyinī ca hoti varādāyinī ca kāyassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a female noble disciple who grows in five ways grows nobly, "
"taking on what is essential and excellent in this life."

msgctxt "an5.64:1.2"
msgid "Katamāhi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.64:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhāya vaḍḍhati, sīlena vaḍḍhati, sutena vaḍḍhati, cāgena vaḍḍhati, "
"paññāya vaḍḍhati—"
msgstr "She grows in faith, ethics, learning, generosity, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an5.64:1.4"
msgid ""
"imāhi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhamānā ariyasāvikā ariyāya "
"vaḍḍhiyā vaḍḍhati, sārādāyinī ca hoti varādāyinī ca kāyassāti."
msgstr ""
"A female noble disciple who grows in these five ways grows nobly, taking on "
"what is essential and excellent in this life."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: ca yā pavaḍḍhati → yādha vaḍḍhati (bj)
msgctxt "an5.64:2.1"
msgid "Saddhāya sīlena ca yā pavaḍḍhati,"
msgstr "She who grows in faith and ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.64:2.2"
msgid "Paññāya cāgena sutena cūbhayaṃ;"
msgstr "wisdom, and both generosity and learning—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.64:2.3"
msgid "Sā tādisī sīlavatī upāsikā,"
msgstr "a virtuous laywoman such as she"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.64:2.4"
msgid "Ādīyatī sāramidheva attano”ti."
msgstr "takes on what is essential for herself in this life.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.64:2.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
